node.text:
1 year to go before the Rugby World Cup 2022 in South Africa! 

As the Official Timekeeper of Rugby World Cup Sevens 2022, TUDOR extends its successful partnership with World Rugby. With the tournament heading to the African continent for the first time, TUDOR will celebrate daring moments of action at the event, as part of their successful #BornToDare series. World Rugby and TUDOR will work in partnership to push the boundaries of new horizons and drive a new, electrifying period for the sport. 

@rugbyworldcup #Tudorwatch #BornToDare #RWC2022 

http://www.tudorwatch.com/ambassadors/rugby

node.title: One year to go - Rugby World Cup
